Kubernetes Interview Questions
================================

Suppoes, I have deploymemnt of "nginx", i want to expose that deployment publically on port 443 what will you do?

- create a file in docker and specify the details of port into specification section and run the command 
 and inside kind : Deployement
 - kubectl apply -f abc.yml 
 

