Q - how will you increase the replica-set
- In replica-set .yml file we set kind:Replica-set and specific section we set Replicas: 4 
and run kubectl apply -f replicaset.yml



-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Q - how to rollback the things on previous release?
- kubectl rollout history deployment my-training
- kubectl rollout undo deployment my-training
 - rollback to previous one


